def max_weapons_carried(p, f, cnt_s, cnt_w, s, w):
    if s >= w:
        (s, w) = (w, s)
        (cnt_s, cnt_w) = (cnt_w, cnt_s)

    def calculate_max_weapons(x):
        res = x
        cur_a = p - x * s
        y = min(f // s, cnt_s - x)
        res += y
        cur_b = f - y * s
        p_w = min(cur_a // w, cnt_w)
        res += p_w
        q_w = min(cur_b // w, cnt_w - p_w)
        res += q_w
        return res
    limit = p // s
    max_weapons = 0
    for j in range(min(limit, cnt_s), -1, -1):
        ans = calculate_max_weapons(j)
        if ans > max_weapons:
            max_weapons = ans
    return max_weapons
